# Screenshots Directory

This directory is for storing README screenshots and visual documentation.

## Guidelines

- Use descriptive filenames (e.g., `hero-section-desktop.png`, `analytics-dashboard.png`)
- Optimize images before committing (use TinyPNG or Squoosh)
- Recommended formats: PNG for UI, WebP for photos
- Maximum file size: 500KB per image
- Include both desktop and mobile views where applicable
